articles.title: Over 150 false killer whales stranded on Australia beach cannot be saved, experts say - CBS News
articles.description: Marine experts have given up hope of rescuing 157 false killer whales that stranded on a remote Australian beach.
articles.content:
Marine experts have given up hope of rescuing more than 150 false killer whales that stranded on a remote beach on Australia's island state of Tasmania, officials said on Wednesday.
